  'cs_se_02', 'cs_software_engineering', 13,
  'Quy trÃ¬nh & MÃ´ hÃ¬nh PhÃ¡t triá»ƒn',
  'TuyÃªn ngÃ´n Agile & Há»‡ phÆ°Æ¡ng phÃ¡p Scrum',
  E'## 1. TuyÃªn ngÃ´n Agile (2001)\n\n17 láº­p trÃ¬nh viÃªn ná»•i tiáº¿ng gáº·p nhau táº¡i Snowbird, Utah vÃ  viáº¿t **Agile Manifesto** â€” tuyÃªn bá»‘ 4 giÃ¡ trá»‹ vÃ  12 nguyÃªn táº¯c Ä‘á»‹nh hÃ¬nh láº¡i ngÃ nh pháº§n má»m hiá»‡n Ä‘áº¡i.\n\n### 4 GiÃ¡ trá»‹ cá»‘t lÃµi\n\n| Äá» cao | HÆ¡n |\n|--------|-----|\n| **CÃ¡ nhÃ¢n & tÆ°Æ¡ng tÃ¡c** | Quy trÃ¬nh & cÃ´ng cá»¥ |\n| **Pháº§n má»m cháº¡y tá»‘t** | TÃ i liá»‡u Ä‘áº§y Ä‘á»§ |\n| **Cá»™ng tÃ¡c vá»›i khÃ¡ch hÃ ng** | ThÆ°Æ¡ng lÆ°á»£ng há»£p Ä‘á»“ng |\n| **Pháº£n há»“i vá»›i thay Ä‘á»•i** | TuÃ¢n thá»§ káº¿ hoáº¡ch |\n\n> âš ï¸ **Hiá»ƒu Ä‘Ãºng:** Agile *khÃ´ng cÃ³ nghÄ©a lÃ * khÃ´ng viáº¿t tÃ i liá»‡u hoáº·c khÃ´ng láº­p káº¿ hoáº¡ch. NÃ³ Æ°u tiÃªn giÃ¡ trá»‹ bÃªn trÃ¡i cao hÆ¡n bÃªn pháº£i, khÃ´ng phá»§ nháº­n bÃªn pháº£i.\n\n### 12 NguyÃªn táº¯c Agile (trÃ­ch lá»c quan trá»ng)\n1. Æ¯u tiÃªn cao nháº¥t lÃ  lÃ m hÃ i lÃ²ng khÃ¡ch hÃ ng qua viá»‡c giao pháº§n má»m sá»›m vÃ  liÃªn tá»¥c.\n2. ChÃ o Ä‘Ã³n thay Ä‘á»•i yÃªu cáº§u â€” dÃ¹ muá»™n trong quÃ¡ trÃ¬nh phÃ¡t triá»ƒn.\n3. Giao pháº§n má»m cháº¡y Ä‘Æ°á»£c thÆ°á»ng xuyÃªn (vÃ i tuáº§n Ä‘áº¿n vÃ i thÃ¡ng, ngáº¯n hÆ¡n thÃ¬ tá»‘t hÆ¡n).\n4. Dev vÃ  business cá»™ng tÃ¡c hÃ ng ngÃ y trong suá»‘t dá»± Ã¡n.\n5. ÄÆ¡n giáº£n â€” tá»‘i Ä‘a hÃ³a lÆ°á»£ng cÃ´ng viá»‡c khÃ´ng cáº§n lÃ m.\n\n---\n\n## 2. Framework Scrum\n\nScrum lÃ  framework phá»• biáº¿n nháº¥t Ä‘á»ƒ triá»ƒn khai Agile, chiáº¿m ~58% adoption theo VersionOne Survey 2023.\n\n### CÃ¡c vai trÃ² (Scrum Roles)\n\n```\nâ”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”\nâ”‚              SCRUM TEAM                          â”‚\nâ”‚  â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”  â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”  â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â” â”‚\nâ”‚  â”‚Product Ownerâ”‚  â”‚ Scrum Master â”‚  â”‚Dev Team â”‚ â”‚\nâ”‚  â”‚  (PO)       â”‚  â”‚    (SM)      â”‚  â”‚ (3-9)   â”‚ â”‚\nâ”‚  â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜  â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜  â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜ â”‚\nâ””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜\n```\n\n**Product Owner (PO):**\n- Äáº¡i diá»‡n tiáº¿ng nÃ³i cá»§a khÃ¡ch hÃ ng vÃ  stakeholders.\n- Quáº£n lÃ½ **Product Backlog**: danh sÃ¡ch Æ°u tiÃªn táº¥t cáº£ tÃ­nh nÄƒng cáº§n lÃ m.\n- Quyáº¿t Ä‘á»‹nh **"What"** (lÃ m gÃ¬) â€” khÃ´ng quyáº¿t Ä‘á»‹nh "How" (lÃ m tháº¿ nÃ o).\n- Chá»‹u trÃ¡ch nhiá»‡m ROI (Return on Investment) cá»§a sáº£n pháº©m.\n\n**Scrum Master (SM):**\n- *Servant-leader* â€” phá»¥c vá»¥ team, khÃ´ng pháº£i quáº£n lÃ½.\n- Loáº¡i bá» **blockers** (váº­t cáº£n) ngÄƒn team lÃ m viá»‡c hiá»‡u quáº£.\n- Äáº£m báº£o team hiá»ƒu vÃ  thá»±c hÃ nh Scrum Ä‘Ãºng.\n- **KhÃ´ng pháº£i** lÃ  project manager, khÃ´ng giao task cho dev.\n\n**Development Team:**\n- Tá»± tá»• chá»©c (self-organizing): tá»± quyáº¿t Ä‘á»‹nh cÃ¡ch hoÃ n thÃ nh cÃ´ng viá»‡c.\n- Äa nÄƒng (cross-functional): cÃ³ Ä‘á»§ ká»¹ nÄƒng Ä‘á»ƒ deliver pháº§n má»m cháº¡y Ä‘Æ°á»£c.\n- LÃ½ tÆ°á»Ÿng 3â€“9 ngÆ°á»i â€” Ä‘á»§ nhá» Ä‘á»ƒ giao tiáº¿p hiá»‡u quáº£, Ä‘á»§ lá»›n Ä‘á»ƒ cÃ³ Ä‘á»§ ká»¹ nÄƒng.\n\n### CÃ¡c sá»± kiá»‡n Scrum (Sprint Ceremonies)\n\n| Sá»± kiá»‡n | Táº§n suáº¥t | Thá»i gian tá»‘i Ä‘a | Má»¥c Ä‘Ã­ch |\n|---------|----------|-----------------|----------|\n| **Sprint Planning** | Äáº§u má»—i Sprint | 8h (Sprint 4 tuáº§n) | Chá»n PBI, táº¡o Sprint Backlog |\n| **Daily Standup** | Má»—i ngÃ y | 15 phÃºt | Sync, phÃ¡t hiá»‡n blocker |\n| **Sprint Review** | Cuá»‘i Sprint | 4h | Demo cho stakeholders |\n| **Sprint Retrospective** | Cuá»‘i Sprint | 3h | Cáº£i thiá»‡n quy trÃ¬nh team |\n\n### Sprint lÃ  gÃ¬?\n\nSprint lÃ  **timebox** cá»‘ Ä‘á»‹nh (1â€“4 tuáº§n, thÆ°á»ng 2 tuáº§n) trong Ä‘Ã³ team táº¡o ra má»™t **Increment** â€” pháº§n má»m cÃ³ thá»ƒ release Ä‘Æ°á»£c (potentially shippable product).\n\n```\nProduct Backlog\nâ”‚\nâ”œâ”€â”€ Sprint Planning\nâ”‚         â”‚\nâ”‚    Sprint Backlog\nâ”‚         â”‚\nâ”‚    [Sprint 2 tuáº§n]\nâ”‚    Day 1 â”€ Daily Standup\nâ”‚    Day 2 â”€ Daily Standup\nâ”‚    ...      Development\nâ”‚    Day N â”€ Daily Standup\nâ”‚         â”‚\nâ”œâ”€â”€ Sprint Review (Demo)\nâ”œâ”€â”€ Sprint Retrospective\nâ”‚         â”‚\nâ””â”€â”€ Increment (Done)\n```\n\n### Definition of Done (DoD)\nMá»™t user story chá»‰ Ä‘Æ°á»£c coi lÃ  "Done" khi:\n- Code review passed.\n- Unit test viáº¿t vÃ  pass.\n- Integration test pass.\n- Deploy lÃªn staging thÃ nh cÃ´ng.\n- PO accept.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Scrum vs. Waterfall â€” Táº¡i sao Scrum tháº¯ng?\n\n| TÃ¬nh huá»‘ng | Waterfall | Scrum |\n|-----------|-----------|-------|\n| YÃªu cáº§u thay Ä‘á»•i tuáº§n 6 | Pháº£i quay láº¡i tá»« Ä‘áº§u | ÄÆ°a vÃ o Backlog Sprint sau |\n| KhÃ¡ch hÃ ng tháº¥y sáº£n pháº©m | ThÃ¡ng 12 (cuá»‘i) | ThÃ¡ng 1 (Sprint 1) |\n| PhÃ¡t hiá»‡n lá»—i thiáº¿t káº¿ muá»™n | Chi phÃ­ x100 | Chi phÃ­ x1 (fix ngay Sprint sau) |\n| Team cÃ³ thÃ nh viÃªn rá»i | Dá»± Ã¡n trá»… | Scrum Master Ä‘iá»u chá»‰nh velocity |',
  'core-theory',
  '["Spotify Model: Chia team thÃ nh Squads (nhÆ° Scrum team), Tribes (nhÃ³m Squad cÃ¹ng domain), Chapters (nhÃ³m cÃ¹ng ká»¹ nÄƒng), Guilds (cá»™ng Ä‘á»“ng chia sáº» kiáº¿n thá»©c). ÄÃ¢y lÃ  Scrum Ä‘Æ°á»£c scale lÃªn tá»• chá»©c lá»›n.", "Amazon dÃ¹ng 2-pizza rule: má»—i team khÃ´ng Ä‘Æ°á»£c lá»›n hÆ¡n sá»‘ ngÆ°á»i cÃ³ thá»ƒ Äƒn no vá»›i 2 chiáº¿c pizza â€” tÆ°Æ¡ng Ä‘Æ°Æ¡ng Dev Team 6-8 ngÆ°á»i trong Scrum."]'::jsonb,
