  E'## 1. PhÃ¢n loáº¡i YÃªu cáº§u\n\nYÃªu cáº§u pháº§n má»m chia thÃ nh 2 loáº¡i chÃ­nh:\n\n### YÃªu cáº§u Chá»©c nÄƒng (Functional Requirements â€” FR)\n- MÃ´ táº£ **há»‡ thá»‘ng lÃ m gÃ¬** â€” cÃ¡c chá»©c nÄƒng cá»¥ thá»ƒ.\n- VÃ­ dá»¥: "NgÆ°á»i dÃ¹ng cÃ³ thá»ƒ Ä‘Äƒng nháº­p báº±ng email vÃ  máº­t kháº©u", "Há»‡ thá»‘ng gá»­i email xÃ¡c nháº­n sau khi Ä‘áº·t hÃ ng".\n- Ghi láº¡i trong **Software Requirements Specification (SRS)**.\n\n### YÃªu cáº§u Phi chá»©c nÄƒng (Non-Functional Requirements â€” NFR)\n- MÃ´ táº£ **há»‡ thá»‘ng váº­n hÃ nh tháº¿ nÃ o** â€” cháº¥t lÆ°á»£ng vÃ  rÃ ng buá»™c.\n- PhÃ¢n loáº¡i theo mÃ´ hÃ¬nh **FURPS+**:\n\n| Loáº¡i | VÃ­ dá»¥ |\n|------|-------|\n| **F**unctionality | Báº£o máº­t: mÃ£ hÃ³a AES-256 |\n| **U**sability | NgÆ°á»i dÃ¹ng hoÃ n thÃ nh checkout trong < 3 bÆ°á»›c |\n| **R**eliability | Uptime 99.9% (downtime < 8.7h/nÄƒm) |\n| **P**erformance | Response time < 200ms cho 95% request |\n| **S**upportability | CÃ³ thá»ƒ deploy má»›i trong < 1 giá» |\n\n---\n\n## 2. User Stories\n\nUser Story lÃ  cÃ¡ch viáº¿t yÃªu cáº§u theo gÃ³c nhÃ¬n ngÆ°á»i dÃ¹ng trong Agile:\n\n```\nAs a [role], I want [feature] so that [benefit]\n(LÃ  [vai trÃ²], tÃ´i muá»‘n [tÃ­nh nÄƒng] Ä‘á»ƒ [lá»£i Ã­ch])\n```\n\n**VÃ­ dá»¥ thá»±c táº¿:**\n- *LÃ  há»c sinh, tÃ´i muá»‘n xem Ä‘iá»ƒm sá»‘ ngay sau khi ná»™p bÃ i Ä‘á»ƒ biáº¿t mÃ¬nh cáº§n Ã´n táº­p gÃ¬.*\n- *LÃ  giÃ¡o viÃªn, tÃ´i muá»‘n xuáº¥t bÃ¡o cÃ¡o lá»›p sang Excel Ä‘á»ƒ ná»™p cho nhÃ  trÆ°á»ng.*\n\n### TiÃªu chÃ­ INVEST cho User Story tá»‘t\n| Chá»¯ cÃ¡i | NghÄ©a | Ã nghÄ©a |\n|---------|-------|----------|\n| **I** | Independent | Story Ä‘á»™c láº­p, khÃ´ng phá»¥ thuá»™c story khÃ¡c |\n| **N** | Negotiable | CÃ³ thá»ƒ thÆ°Æ¡ng lÆ°á»£ng chi tiáº¿t |\n| **V** | Valuable | Mang giÃ¡ trá»‹ rÃµ rÃ ng cho ngÆ°á»i dÃ¹ng |\n| **E** | Estimable | CÃ³ thá»ƒ Æ°á»›c tÃ­nh effort |\n| **S** | Small | LÃ m xong trong 1 Sprint |\n| **T** | Testable | CÃ³ tiÃªu chÃ­ rÃµ rÃ ng Ä‘á»ƒ kiá»ƒm tra done |\n\n---\n\n## 3. UML Use Case Diagram\n\nSÆ¡ Ä‘á»“ Use Case thá»ƒ hiá»‡n **ai (Actor) lÃ m gÃ¬ (Use Case) vá»›i há»‡ thá»‘ng**.\n\n```\n          â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”\n          â”‚         <<System>>          â”‚\n          â”‚                             â”‚\nKhÃ¡ch â”€â”€oâ”€â”¤â”€â”€ TÃ¬m kiáº¿m sáº£n pháº©m         â”‚\nhÃ ng     â”‚                             â”‚\n    â”€â”€oâ”€â”€â”¤â”€â”€ ThÃªm vÃ o giá» hÃ ng         â”‚\n          â”‚         â†‘                   â”‚\n          â”‚    <<include>>              â”‚\n          â”‚         â”‚                   â”‚\n    â”€â”€oâ”€â”€â”¤â”€â”€ Thanh toÃ¡n â”€â”€<<extend>>â”€â”€â”€â”¤â”€â”€ Thanh toÃ¡n tráº£ gÃ³p\n          â”‚                             â”‚\nAdmin â”€â”€oâ”€â”¤â”€â”€ Quáº£n lÃ½ sáº£n pháº©m          â”‚\n          â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜\n```\n\n**Quan há»‡ trong Use Case:**\n- **`<<include>>`**: Use Case A luÃ´n gá»i Use Case B (báº¯t buá»™c). *VÃ­ dá»¥: Thanh toÃ¡n include XÃ¡c thá»±c OTP.*\n- **`<<extend>>`**: Use Case B cÃ³ thá»ƒ má»Ÿ rá»™ng A (tÃ¹y chá»n). *VÃ­ dá»¥: Thanh toÃ¡n extend Thanh toÃ¡n tráº£ gÃ³p.*\n- **Generalization**: Actor con káº¿ thá»«a quan há»‡ cá»§a Actor cha.\n\n---\n\n## 4. UML Class Diagram\n\nClass Diagram thá»ƒ hiá»‡n **cáº¥u trÃºc tÄ©nh** â€” cÃ¡c lá»›p vÃ  quan há»‡ giá»¯a chÃºng.\n\n```\nâ”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”         â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”\nâ”‚    Customer     â”‚         â”‚     Order       â”‚\nâ”œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”¤  1   *  â”œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”¤\nâ”‚ -id: int        â”‚â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”‚ -orderId: int   â”‚\nâ”‚ -name: String   â”‚ places  â”‚ -date: Date     â”‚\nâ”‚ -email: String  â”‚         â”‚ -status: String â”‚\nâ”œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”¤         â”œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”¤\nâ”‚ +login()        â”‚         â”‚ +getTotal()     â”‚\nâ”‚ +getOrders()    â”‚         â”‚ +cancel()       â”‚\nâ””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜         â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜\n```\n\n**CÃ¡c loáº¡i quan há»‡ trong Class Diagram:**\n| Quan há»‡ | KÃ½ hiá»‡u | Ã nghÄ©a | VÃ­ dá»¥ |\n|---------|---------|---------|-------|\n| **Association** | â”€â”€â”€â”€ | A cÃ³ liÃªn káº¿t vá»›i B | Customer places Order |\n| **Aggregation** | â—‡â”€â”€â”€â”€ | A chá»©a B (B tá»“n táº¡i Ä‘á»™c láº­p) | Library has Books |\n| **Composition** | â—†â”€â”€â”€â”€ | A sá»Ÿ há»¯u B (B khÃ´ng tá»“n táº¡i náº¿u khÃ´ng cÃ³ A) | House has Rooms |\n| **Inheritance** | â”€â”€â–· | B káº¿ thá»«a A | Dog extends Animal |\n| **Dependency** | ----â–· | A dÃ¹ng B táº¡m thá»i | Controller uses Request |',
  'core-theory',
  '["Jira lÃ  cÃ´ng cá»¥ phá»• biáº¿n nháº¥t Ä‘á»ƒ quáº£n lÃ½ User Stories vÃ  Sprint Backlog trong thá»±c táº¿. Má»—i story cÃ³ Story Points (1, 2, 3, 5, 8, 13 â€” dÃ£y Fibonacci) Ä‘á»ƒ Æ°á»›c tÃ­nh Ä‘á»™ phá»©c táº¡p.", "draw.io vÃ  Lucidchart lÃ  2 cÃ´ng cá»¥ váº½ UML miá»…n phÃ­ phá»• biáº¿n nháº¥t trong industry. PlantUML cho phÃ©p viáº¿t UML báº±ng text code â€” ráº¥t tiá»‡n cho developer."]'::jsonb,
  '["YÃªu cáº§u phi chá»©c nÄƒng (NFR) thÆ°á»ng quyáº¿t Ä‘á»‹nh kiáº¿n trÃºc há»‡ thá»‘ng nhiá»u hÆ¡n yÃªu cáº§u chá»©c nÄƒng â€” vÃ­ dá»¥ NFR performance 100k concurrent users buá»™c pháº£i dÃ¹ng microservices.", "Trong Use Case, Actor khÃ´ng nháº¥t thiáº¿t lÃ  con ngÆ°á»i â€” há»‡ thá»‘ng bÃªn ngoÃ i nhÆ° Payment Gateway cÅ©ng lÃ  Actor.", "Composition máº¡nh hÆ¡n Aggregation: náº¿u xÃ³a House, Room cÅ©ng biáº¿n máº¥t; náº¿u xÃ³a Library, Book váº«n cÃ³ thá»ƒ tá»“n táº¡i trong kho khÃ¡c."]'::jsonb,
