  'cs_se_04', 'cs_software_engineering', 13,
  'Kiáº¿n trÃºc & Máº«u thiáº¿t káº¿ (Design Patterns)',
  'Kiáº¿n trÃºc pháº§n má»m: Monolith, Microservices vÃ  mÃ´ hÃ¬nh MVC',
  E'## 1. Kiáº¿n trÃºc Monolith (NguyÃªn khá»‘i)\n\nToÃ n bá»™ á»©ng dá»¥ng Ä‘Æ°á»£c Ä‘Ã³ng gÃ³i vÃ  deploy nhÆ° **má»™t Ä‘Æ¡n vá»‹ duy nháº¥t**.\n\n```\nâ”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”\nâ”‚              Monolith App              â”‚\nâ”‚  â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â” â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â” â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â” â”‚\nâ”‚  â”‚  Module  â”‚ â”‚  Module  â”‚ â”‚ Module â”‚ â”‚\nâ”‚  â”‚   User   â”‚ â”‚  Order   â”‚ â”‚Payment â”‚ â”‚\nâ”‚  â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜ â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜ â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜ â”‚\nâ”‚         Shared Database                â”‚\nâ””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜\n             Deploy cÃ¹ng lÃºc\n```\n\n**Æ¯u Ä‘iá»ƒm:**\n- ÄÆ¡n giáº£n Ä‘á»ƒ develop, test, debug ban Ä‘áº§u.\n- Giao tiáº¿p giá»¯a cÃ¡c module lÃ  function call â€” nhanh, khÃ´ng cÃ³ network overhead.\n- Deploy 1 láº§n duy nháº¥t.\n\n**NhÆ°á»£c Ä‘iá»ƒm khi scale:**\n- Scale toÃ n bá»™ app dÃ¹ chá»‰ 1 module bá»‹ quÃ¡ táº£i (khÃ´ng thá»ƒ scale riÃªng).\n- Thay Ä‘á»•i nhá» â†’ pháº£i build vÃ  deploy toÃ n bá»™ app â†’ rá»§i ro cao.\n- Sau nhiá»u nÄƒm phÃ¡t triá»ƒn dá»… trá»Ÿ thÃ nh **"Big Ball of Mud"** â€” code rá»‘i khÃ´ng thá»ƒ maintain.\n- Má»™t lá»—i nghiÃªm trá»ng cÃ³ thá»ƒ lÃ m sáº­p toÃ n bá»™ há»‡ thá»‘ng.\n\n---\n\n## 2. Kiáº¿n trÃºc Microservices\n\nChia nhá» á»©ng dá»¥ng thÃ nh cÃ¡c **service Ä‘á»™c láº­p**, má»—i service tá»± quáº£n lÃ½ database vÃ  deploy riÃªng.\n\n```\n        â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”\n        â”‚         API Gateway          â”‚\n        â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜\n               /        |        \\\n        â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”    â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”    â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”\n        â”‚ User â”‚    â”‚ Order â”‚    â”‚ Payment â”‚\n        â”‚ Svc  â”‚    â”‚  Svc  â”‚    â”‚   Svc   â”‚\n        â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜    â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜    â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜\n          DB1          DB2          DB3\n```\n\n**Æ¯u Ä‘iá»ƒm:**\n- Scale Ä‘á»™c láº­p: náº¿u Payment Svc quÃ¡ táº£i â†’ scale riÃªng Payment mÃ  khÃ´ng áº£nh hÆ°á»Ÿng User Svc.\n- Deploy Ä‘á»™c láº­p: team Payment deploy khÃ´ng áº£nh hÆ°á»Ÿng team Order.\n- CÃ³ thá»ƒ dÃ¹ng ngÃ´n ngá»¯/DB khÃ¡c nhau cho tá»«ng service (polyglot persistence).\n- Má»™t service fail khÃ´ng lÃ m sáº­p toÃ n bá»™ há»‡ thá»‘ng (náº¿u cÃ³ circuit breaker).\n\n**NhÆ°á»£c Ä‘iá»ƒm:**\n- Phá»©c táº¡p hÆ¡n: distributed transactions, eventual consistency, service discovery.\n- Network latency giá»¯a cÃ¡c service (so vá»›i function call trong monolith).\n- Cáº§n DevOps máº¡nh: Kubernetes, Docker, CI/CD pipeline cho tá»«ng service.\n- Debugging khÃ³ hÆ¡n: pháº£i dÃ¹ng distributed tracing (Jaeger, Zipkin).\n\n### Khi nÃ o chá»n gÃ¬?\n| TiÃªu chÃ­ | Monolith | Microservices |\n|----------|----------|---------------|\n| Team size | < 10 ngÆ°á»i | > 20 ngÆ°á»i |\n| Giai Ä‘oáº¡n | MVP/Startup | Scale up |\n| YÃªu cáº§u scale | Äá»u nhau | KhÃ´ng Ä‘á»“ng Ä‘á»u |\n| Budget DevOps | Tháº¥p | Cao |\n\n> ðŸ’¡ **Thá»±c táº¿:** Amazon, Netflix, Uber Ä‘á»u báº¯t Ä‘áº§u báº±ng Monolith rá»“i chuyá»ƒn sang Microservices khi scale cáº§n thiáº¿t.\n\n---\n\n## 3. MÃ´ hÃ¬nh MVC (Model-View-Controller)\n\nMVC lÃ  pattern kiáº¿n trÃºc phÃ¢n tÃ¡ch á»©ng dá»¥ng thÃ nh 3 layer:\n\n```\n           Request\n User â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â†’ Controller\n                           â”‚\n                      Cáº­p nháº­t\n                    â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”´â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”\n                  Model         View\n                (dá»¯ liá»‡u)    (giao diá»‡n)\n                    â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”¬â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜\n                      Tráº£ vá»\n                           â”‚\n User â†â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€\n           Response\n```\n\n| Component | Nhiá»‡m vá»¥ | VÃ­ dá»¥ |\n|-----------|---------|-------|\n| **Model** | Business logic + data | UserModel, OrderModel, DB queries |\n| **View** | Hiá»ƒn thá»‹ giao diá»‡n | HTML template, React component |\n| **Controller** | Nháº­n request, gá»i Model, chá»n View | UserController.login() |\n\n**Æ¯u Ä‘iá»ƒm MVC:**\n- TÃ¡ch biá»‡t concerns â†’ dá»… test tá»«ng pháº§n Ä‘á»™c láº­p.\n- Team phÃ¢n cÃ´ng rÃµ rÃ ng: backend dev lÃ m Model+Controller, frontend dev lÃ m View.\n- CÃ³ thá»ƒ thay View (web â†’ mobile) mÃ  khÃ´ng Ä‘á»•i Model.\n\n**Framework phá»• biáº¿n dÃ¹ng MVC:**\n- Web: Ruby on Rails, Laravel (PHP), ASP.NET MVC, Spring MVC (Java)\n- Desktop: Android MVC (legacy), WPF (C#)',
  'core-theory',
  '["Netflix dÃ¹ng > 700 microservices. Há» ná»•i tiáº¿ng vá»›i Chaos Monkey â€” tool tá»± Ä‘á»™ng kill random service trong production Ä‘á»ƒ kiá»ƒm tra Ä‘á»™ bá»n há»‡ thá»‘ng.", "Django vÃ  Flask (Python) Ã¡p dá»¥ng biáº¿n thá»ƒ MVT (Model-View-Template) â€” gáº§n giá»‘ng MVC nhÆ°ng Template thay Controller xá»­ lÃ½ routing."]'::jsonb,
  '["Microservices giáº£i quyáº¿t váº¥n Ä‘á» organizational scaling â€” khÃ´ng chá»‰ technical scaling: Conway Law nÃ³i kiáº¿n trÃºc há»‡ thá»‘ng pháº£n Ã¡nh cáº¥u trÃºc tá»• chá»©c team.", "API Gateway trong Microservices khÃ´ng chá»‰ lÃ  load balancer â€” nÃ³ cÃ²n xá»­ lÃ½ auth, rate limiting, request aggregation (fan-out) vÃ  response caching.", "MVC khÃ´ng pháº£i pattern duy nháº¥t: MVVM phá»• biáº¿n vá»›i frontend reactive (Angular, Vue), MVP dÃ¹ng trong Android."]'::jsonb,
